data.title: P & B
data.meta_description: Where to watch P & B (1983) starring Stellan Skarsgrd, Allan Edwall, Lena Nyman and directed by Hans Alfredson.
data.text: Pettersson and Bendel are both worn, run-down and broke. Despite this they decide to start a business and become rich. Unexperienced they are open to any deal. They tamper, scam and exploit loopholes that exist.
